 boundaries between cooking, eating, and lounging dissolve, creating a multi-purpose living space that reflects the owner’s love for cooking and entertaining. A custom-made sofa anchors this area, serving both as a statement piece and a functional divider between the dining and living zones.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=559904\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-559904\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-4-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen and living area with a blue and white color scheme, featuring a blue marble dining table, blue cabinetry, built-in appliances, and a beige sofa with a glass block wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-4-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-4-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-4-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-4-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-4-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOne of the most notable changes is the repositioning of the apartment’s entrance. The new entryway functions as a welcoming threshold, subtly separating the outside world from the interior of the home. The space, previously occupied by the kitchen, now serves as a multifunctional zone with storage, a seating area, and even a laundry space tucked away discreetly. This thoughtful use of space exemplifies the design’s attention to functionality, even in the smallest details.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=559905\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-559905\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-5-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with a minimalist design features a beige sofa, flat-screen TV, blue pendant light, glass block wall, and large sliding glass doors with sheer curtains.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-5-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-5-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-5-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=559906\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-559906\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-6-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Solid blue kitchen cabinet with integrated oven and drawers, adjacent to a wall of glass blocks.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-6-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-6-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-6-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/