 facing a wall-mounted TV. A blue pendant light hangs above, and large windows provide natural light. Minimalist decor includes a small table with a vase.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-9-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-9-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-9-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=559910\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-559910\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-10-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A person in a white robe relaxes on a balcony chair, basking in the sun. The room has a sofa, a small table with decor, and a TV. A window shows an urban view with buildings and antennas.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-10-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-10-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-10-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href