src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-16-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A rooftop balcony with a blue table and chair set, potted plants, and city views under a clear sky.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-16-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-16-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-16-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-16-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-16-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe outdoor space, nearly half the size of the apartment itself, has been transformed into an extension of the living area, complete with an urban garden and a water feature. The enlarged opening from the sitting area to the balcony not only connects the interior and exterior spaces but also frames views of Athens’ Hymettus and Lycabettus mountains.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=559917\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-559917\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-17-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern balcony with a blue sectional sofa, round wooden table holding mugs, potted plants, and a view of city buildings and mountains in the background.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Kyano-Apartment-Athens-Greece-Space-Is-Around-Us-17-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://d